author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
After seeing the original Green Goblin costume from Sam Raimi's Spider-Man last year, Adam finally get an audience with an original Spider-Man costume from that groundbreaking trilogy. This is the black symbiote costume made for Spider-Man 3, and the culmination of the Raimi Spider-Man suit designs. The layers of dimensionality seen up close are stunning, and we finally get to see where the zippers are on this costume!

Learn more about this prop and see more details at: https://propstoreauction.com/auctions/info/id/462
The Spider-Man Green Goblin costume: https://youtu.be/u0023BuAX5g

Shot by Josh Self and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
